  "narrative": {
    "theme_description": "The Sunken Crypt is the ancient burial site of the first Guardian \u2014 a warrior who sealed the Hollow by absorbing part of its corruption. Over centuries, the Hollow corrupted the Guardian, transforming them into the Hollow Warden. The crypt's flooded halls are haunted by the undead remains of those who came to pay respects and never left.",
    "room_text_pool": [
      {
        "text": "Stone murals line the walls, depicting a warrior driving back a tide of darkness. The paint is faded but the story is clear.",
        "type": "event"
      },
      {
        "text": "Water seeps through cracks in the stone ceiling, dripping into stagnant pools. The smell of decay is overwhelming.",
        "type": "combat"
      },
      {
        "text": "Rows of stone sarcophagi line the walls, their lids askew. Bones are scattered across the flooded floor.",
        "type": "combat"
      },
      {
        "text": "A pristine altar sits untouched amidst the decay. An offering bowl still holds dried flowers. You feel a sense of calm.",
        "type": "rest"
      },
      {
        "text": "The water here is waist-deep and dark. Something shifts beneath the surface.",
        "type": "combat"
      },
      {
        "text": "Wall carvings depict the Guardian's sacrifice \u2014 hands pressed against a seal, violet light pouring through the cracks. Below, in careful script: 'The Warden's armor weakens when the braziers are lit.'",
        "type": "event"
      },
      {
        "text": "A rotted bookshelf holds scrolls, most disintegrated beyond reading. One remains intact, sealed in wax.",
        "type": "treasure"
      },
      {
        "text": "Two iron braziers flank a heavy door. They are cold and dark, but oil still pools in their basins.",
        "type": "event"
      },
      {
        "text": "The chamber is vast. At its center stands an armored figure, motionless, wreathed in faint violet light. The Hollow Warden.",
        "type": "boss"
      },
      {
        "text": "Beyond the Warden's chamber, a vault door hangs open. Inside, weapons and relics gleam in the torchlight.",
        "type": "treasure"
      }
    ],
    "lore_pool": [
